    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an adventure across a variety of unique stages set around the world, each reflecting its own distinctive culture and mythology.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328010/extras/0627a79113a0191b6cdb0b19c4fe959b.poster.avif?t=1748140702\" width=798 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328010/extras/0627a79113a0191b6cdb0b19c4fe959b.webm?t=1748140702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328010/extras/0627a79113a0191b6cdb0b19c4fe959b.mp4?t=1748140702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in dynamic boss battles that challenge you to utilize the environment to your advantage. Success depends on choosing the right bullets, charging your weapon strategically, and mastering precise timing for jumps and slides.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328010/extras/3ef0e71ce6fcff6f30c4924928f6c0c0.poster.avif?t=1748140702\" width=798 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328010/extras/3ef0e71ce6fcff6f30c4924928f6c0c0.webm?t=1748140702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328010/extras/3ef0e71ce6fcff6f30c4924928f6c0c0.mp4?t=1748140702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the fallen heroes of each region as you progress through the stages. By locating their final resting places, you can absorb their powers to aid your journey.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328010/extras/c2e8614427651122c130b95f0c42e700.poster.avif?t=1748140702\" width=798 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328010/extras/c2e8614427651122c130b95f0c42e700.webm?t=1748140702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328010/extras/c2e8614427651122c130b95f0c42e700.mp4?t=1748140702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Restore your character’s health in a charmingly unique way: by petting cats scattered throughout the levels. Each region features its own distinct feline companion.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328010/extras/111c883b732937602e92058f0118bfa0.poster.avif?t=1748140702\" width=798 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328010/extras/111c883b732937602e92058f0118bfa0.webm?t=1748140702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328010/extras/111c883b732937602e92058f0118bfa0.mp4?t=1748140702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And you'll be looking at Poradora's handsome face throughout your play! WOW!!!<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328010/extras/642ae4c302456164bdae0f1f4d6bb48f.poster.avif?t=1748140702\" width=798 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328010/extras/642ae4c302456164bdae0f1f4d6bb48f.webm?t=1748140702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328010/extras/642ae4c302456164bdae0f1f4d6bb48f.mp4?t=1748140702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
